# Modelfile — tells Ollama how to load your fine-tuned model.
#
# HOW TO USE (after Step 3 in GUIDE.md, once you've downloaded your
# fine-tuned .gguf file from Colab):
#
# 1. Put the downloaded .gguf file in this same folder.
# 2. Edit the FROM line below to match your actual filename.
# 3. Run:  ollama create cbse-study-bot -f Modelfile
# 4. Test: ollama run cbse-study-bot
#
# That's it — "cbse-study-bot" is now a model Ollama can run, just like
# llama3.2:3b, except it's YOUR fine-tuned version.

FROM ./unsloth_model.gguf

# Keeps answers focused and less random — good for a study bot.
PARAMETER temperature 0.4
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

SYSTEM """You are a helpful CBSE Class 11 study assistant. Answer questions clearly and concisely, in a way that helps a student revise for exams. If you're unsure, say so rather than guessing."""
